== 0.4 Oct 26 2019

  * Added Akka TestKit tests.

  * isCorrect now returns tri-valued ResponseCorrectness instead of Boolean.

  * Fixed some minor bugs and removed dead code.


== 0.3.1 Oct 19 2019

 * Refactored many calls to use QuizGroupKey, simplifying parameter lists.


== 0.3 Oct 19 2019

 * Added actor calls for (1) activating a quiz group and (2) removing a quiz item.


== 0.2 Oct 13 2019

 * Removed the userId from all but messages to the actor (the shard region will hold it).

 * Include promptResponseMap in QuizItemViewWithChoices (to minimize network calls).


== 0.1.1 Oct 12 2019

 * The QuizForUserActor is given a unique userId (= persistenceId): supports cluster sharding.

 * A default quiz (English -> German) is used by QuizForUserActor if the type isn't specified.


== 0.1 Oct 5 2019

 * libanius 0.9.8.5.3 was taken and changed considerably to create this new project libanius-akka.

 * There is now an actor that performs the main quiz operations and is used to serialize the quiz.



